Senior Development Geologist / Reservoir Geologist
05 May 2014 04:39 PM - UAE
..This Senior Development Geologist / Reservoir Geologist opening provides you with an opportunity to manage and conduct the reservoir development planning work program to support the asset. Your duties should include the following: - Geological Evaluation - Hands on experience in 2D, 3D static modelling - Asset Evaluation & Acquisition - Field data acquisition and planning - Well planning - Geological Operations A successful candidate should fulfil the following criteria: - 10+ years minimum experience in relevant Geoscience discipline - Have an Degree in Geology, Geophysics or related field - Have working experience on field development studies, asset evaluation and reservoir modelling - Knowledge in Sequence Stratigraphy, Depositional Environment (DOE), Sedimentology (in clastic and carbonate environment) and Structure Geology Interviews in Duba (more...)
